      "text": "The interesting part isn't that they allow AI. It's that they're now testing whether you know which AI to use and when to stop trusting it. https://t.co/rKrzpAmZbU",
      "author_id": "1718576015801204736",
      "username": "saen_dev",
      "name": "Saeed Anwar",
      "created_at": "2026-05-08T05:57:41.000Z",
      "conversation_id": "2052628988162392125",
      "metrics": {
