      },
      "urls": [],
      "mentions": [],
      "hashtags": [],
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/intellinovus/status/2052550313559609738"
    },
    {
      "id": "2052217107023020240",
      "text": "Lots of SMBs try AI pilots that fizzle out. \n\nThe real pain is weak results and still needing more hires. \n\nWhat helps most? \n\nAdd basic fallbacks for failed tasks, easy human checks, and track actual outcomes not just activity.",
      "author_id": "1286152332204359680",
      "username": "intellinovus",
      "name": "Intellinovus",
      "created_at": "2026-05-07T02:41:01.000Z",
      "conversation_id": "2052217107023020240",
      "metrics": {
        "likes": 0,
        "retweets": 0,
        "replies": 0,
        "quotes": 0,
        "impressions": 1,
        "bookmarks": 0
      },
      "urls": [],
      "mentions": [],
      "hashtags": [],
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/intellinovus/status/2052217107023020240"
    },
    {
      "id": "2052176769415795093",
      "text": "At our company we see young founders battling unreliable agent orchestration and rising costs. \n\nIt's a real bummer for them.\n\nMulti-agent systems need better governance.  \n\nThey also need fallbacks to deliver automation that runs without constant monitoring.\n\nNeed help? DM us.",
      "author_id": "1286152332204359680",
      "username": "intellinovus",
      "name": "Intellinovus",
      "created_at": "2026-05-07T00:00:44.000Z",
      "conversation_id": "2052176769415795093",
      "metrics": {
        "likes": 0,
        "retweets": 0,
        "replies": 0,
        "quotes": 0,
        "impressions": 8,
        "bookmarks": 0
      },
      "urls": [],
      "mentions": [],
      "hashtags": [],
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/intellinovus/status/2052176769415795093"
    },
    {
      "id": "2051865536120660341",
      "text": "For SMBs without IT teams, AI hype meets integration headaches. \n\nWe help cut through brittle setups. \n\nKey wins: connecting email, CRM, and accounting into one flow. \n\nLess context switching, more predictable results without extra hires.",
      "author_id": "1286152332204359680",
      "username": "intellinovus",
      "name": "Intellinovus",
      "created_at": "2026-05-06T03:24:00.000Z",
      "conversation_id": "2051865536120660341",
      "metrics": {
        "likes": 0,
        "retweets": 0,
        "replies": 0,
        "quotes": 0,
        "impressions": 4,
        "bookmarks": 0
      },
      "urls": [],
      "mentions": [],
      "hashtags": [],
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/intellinovus/status/2051865536120660341"
    },
    {
      "id": "2051829405077405978",
      "text": "Even with widespread AI use fragmented stacks keep founders in 80-hour weeks. \n\nEmbedded context-aware agents and hyperautomation are unlocking real-time decisions and better orchestration results.",
      "author_id": "1286152332204359680",
      "username": "intellinovus",
      "name": "Intellinovus",
      "created_at": "2026-05-06T01:00:25.000Z",
      "conversation_id": "2051829405077405978",
      "metrics": {
        "likes": 0,
        "retweets": 0,
        "replies": 0,
        "quotes": 0,
        "impressions": 0,
        "bookmarks": 0
      },
      "urls": [],
      "mentions": [],
      "hashtags": [],
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/intellinovus/status/2051829405077405978"
    },
    {
      "id": "2051799267203764619",
      "text": "This week’s AI Signal Brief is about the messy middle of AI workflow automation.\n\nn8n, Codex, OpenAI on AWS, agent memory, Quick Flows, and why implementation still has teeth.\n\nFull issue here:\nhttps://t.co/jOHVpgoTYd https://t.co/faoSfp6nbw",
      "author_id": "1286152332204359680",
      "username": "intellinovus",
      "name": "Intellinovus",
      "created_at": "2026-05-05T23:00:40.000Z",
      "conversation_id": "2051799267203764619",
      "metrics": {
        "likes": 0,
        "retweets": 0,
        "replies": 0,
        "quotes": 0,
        "impressions": 29,
        "bookmarks": 0
      },
      "urls": [
        "https://osishmael.substack.com/p/the-ai-schism",
        "https://x.com/intellinovus/status/2051799267203764619/photo/1"
      ],
      "mentions": [],
      "hashtags": [],
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/intellinovus/status/2051799267203764619"
    },
    {
      "id": "2051633260313129080",
      "text": "If an AI agent can take action, it needs boundaries.\n\nIf it has memory, it needs structure.\n\nIf it touches customers, it needs accountability.\n\nOtherwise you have not built an agent.\n\nYou have built a very expensive intern with root access.",
      "author_id": "1286152332204359680",
      "username": "intellinovus",
      "name": "Intellinovus",
      "created_at": "2026-05-05T12:01:01.000Z",
      "conversation_id": "2051633260313129080",
      "metrics": {
        "likes": 0,
        "retweets": 0,
        "replies": 0,
        "quotes": 0,
        "impressions": 3,
        "bookmarks": 0
      },
      "urls": [],
      "mentions": [],
      "hashtags": [],
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/intellinovus/status/2051633260313129080"
    },
    {
      "id": "2051511957056798998",
      "text": "Small biz means small team + endless tasks\n\nYou as the owner losing nights to manual ops. \n\nTop 3 automation wins for you.. invoice chasing, customer follow-ups, and inventory alerts. \n\nReliable agents free you to grow the business instead of running it manually.",
      "author_id": "1286152332204359680",
      "username": "intellinovus",
      "name": "Intellinovus",
      "created_at": "2026-05-05T03:59:00.000Z",
      "conversation_id": "2051511957056798998",
      "metrics": {
        "likes": 1,
        "retweets": 0,
        "replies": 1,
        "quotes": 0,
        "impressions": 9,
        "bookmarks": 0
      },
      "urls": [],
      "mentions": [],
      "hashtags": [],
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/intellinovus/status/2051511957056798998"
    },
    {
      "id": "2051451931218817118",
      "text": "The AI is your enthusiastic teammate, not the architect.\n\nIt can help you move faster.\n\nIt can also make confident mistakes at impressive speed.\n\nYou still need to steer the ship.",
      "author_id": "1286152332204359680",
      "username": "intellinovus",
      "name": "Intellinovus",
      "created_at": "2026-05-05T00:00:29.000Z",
      "conversation_id": "2051451931218817118",
      "metrics": {
        "likes": 0,
        "retweets": 0,
        "replies": 0,
        "quotes": 0,
        "impressions": 0,
        "bookmarks": 0
      },
      "urls": [],
      "mentions": [],
      "hashtags": [],
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/intellinovus/status/2051451931218817118"
    },
    {
      "id": "2051119669709250926",
      "text": "One AI workflow worth testing:\n\nUpload document → extract key fields → identify missing info → generate summary → route to human review → create report.\n\nUseful for proposals, invoices, meeting notes, sales briefs, and internal reports.\n\nBoring?\n\nYes.\n\nValuable?\n\nAlso yes.",
      "author_id": "1286152332204359680",
      "username": "intellinovus",
      "name": "Intellinovus",
      "created_at": "2026-05-04T02:00:11.000Z",
