    },
    {
      "id": "2050862972155871246",
      "text": "I'm taking \"AI and the Future of Law\" this quarter, and one of the class discussions was whether lawyers who use AI have a competitive advantage over lawyers who don't. My answer was that, initially, yes, but not once every lawyer is using it.\n\nIf you take two lawyers at the same",
      "author_id": "2843928804",
      "username": "ordonez_adan",
