      "text": "I had a discussion in one of my classes last quarter where my professor said that AI will uncover a \"latent\" legal market.\n\nThis means that people who would not otherwise consume legal services will now do so because the services are more accessible than before.\n\nI think that's https://t.co/TFnekKU2g6",
