      "text": "April was a record month at @Meow with a big number.\n\nWe crossed $2 billion in annualized stablecoin payment volume.\n\nIn addition:\n— All time high ARR\n— Applications up 50% MoM\n— Tracking for millions in profit while hiring faster than ever\n\nWe laid the foundation, now we grow.",
